Beyond the festivities lies a meeting between Tempest and its allies to decide the future of the Nation of Monsters. With the fully revived "Storm Dragon" Veldora, "Ultimate Skill" Raphael, and other powerful comrades, the ruler of the Tempest is confident in taking down his enemies one by one until he can face the man pulling the strings.
